{p}_{n}\in \mathbb{R} 
n
\sum_{n=1}^{∞}\cfrac{1}{{p}_{n}}
\sum_{n=1}^{∞}{p}_{n}\cfrac{{n}^{2}}{{({p}_{1}+{p}_{2}+\dotso+{p}_{n})}^{2}}
P_N=\sum_{n=1}^N p_n\,,\; C=\sum_{n=1}^{+\infty}\frac{1}{p_n}
S_N=\sum_{n=1}^{N}\frac{n^2 p_n}{P_n^2}
S_N < \frac{1}{p_1} + \sum_{n=2}^{N}\frac{n^2(P_n-P_{n-1})}{P_n P_{n-1}} = \frac{5}{p_1}+\sum_{n=2}^{N-1}\frac{2n+1}{P_n}-\frac{N^2}{P_N},
(\clubsuit)
S_N < \frac{2}{p_1} + 4C.
